opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 30th day of March, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the jurists’ names from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
